name: SID 0x10 Diagnostic Session Control - Comprehensive Test Suite
description: Production-grade test suite for UDS Service ID 0x10 (DiagnosticSessionControl) based on ISO 14229-1:2020 Section 9.2. Covers all valid/invalid session transitions, NRC validation, security reset behavior, timing parameters, and complex workflows.

metadata.author: UDS Simulator
metadata.description: ISO 14229-1:2020 Section 9.2 compliant production-grade test suite for SID 0x10 (DiagnosticSessionControl). Based on comprehensive analysis of SID_10_DIAGNOSTIC_SESSION_CONTROL.md, SID_10_PRACTICAL_IMPLEMENTATION.md, and SID_10_SERVICE_INTERACTIONS.md.

notes: Test Suite v2.0.0: Comprehensive production-grade coverage for SID 0x10. Categories: (1) Valid transitions between all 4 sessions including re-entry. (2) Invalid transitions with NRC 0x22 for blocked paths (Extended<->Programming, Programming re-entry, etc.). (3) Subfunction validation covering 0x00, 0x05-0x3F, 0x40-0x5F, 0x60-0x7E, 0x7F. (4) Message length validation. (5) Suppress positive response bit including error case. (6) Security state reset verification on session changes. (7) P2/P2* timing parameter verification. (8) Error recovery from invalid transitions. (9) Service interactions including security access workflow. (10) Edge cases including rapid session changes and S3 timeout prevention. (11) Complete multi-session navigation test.

testCaseDetails.TC-01: Valid session transitions - all paths from Default to other sessions and back, plus Extended/Safety re-entry. All should return positive response 0x50.
testCaseDetails.TC-02: Invalid session transitions - Extended<->Programming, Programming re-entry, Programming<->Safety, Safety<->Extended. All should return NRC 0x22.
testCaseDetails.TC-03: Subfunction validation - boundary values 0x00, 0x05, 0x20, 0x3F, 0x40, 0x5F, 0x60, 0x7E, 0x7F. All should return NRC 0x12.
testCaseDetails.TC-04: Message length validation - missing subfunction and extra bytes. All should return NRC 0x13.
testCaseDetails.TC-05: Suppress positive response bit - 0x81, 0x82, 0x83 should suppress response. 0x82 from Extended should still return NRC 0x22.
testCaseDetails.TC-06: Security reset behavior - security unlocked in Extended resets when changing to Default or re-entering Extended.
testCaseDetails.TC-08: Timing parameters - verify P2 values: Default=50ms, Extended=100ms, Programming=50ms, Safety=50ms. P2*=5000ms for all.
testCaseDetails.TC-09: Error recovery - demonstrates correct recovery path from blocked transition via Default session.
testCaseDetails.TC-10: Service interaction workflows - read operations, security access sequences, proper session/security handling.
testCaseDetails.TC-11: Edge cases - rapid session changes, S3 timeout prevention with Tester Present, stress testing.
testCaseDetails.TC-12: Multi-session navigation - complete round-trip through all sessions via Default hub.
